Detailed Description

cvmx_mio_fus_pll

This register contains PLL Status and controls for the MSC_CLKOUT and MSC_SYS_CLKOUT pins. The fields are reset to zero on a cold reset. the values are preserved on both a warm and soft reset for pass 2.
